latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Posted @withregram • @tiaraindiapageantdiaries
Fashion is not something that exists in dresses only. Fashion is in the sky, in the street, fashion has to do with ideas, the way we live, what is happening. Yes it is said by Coco Chanel and our event photography team @igvibgyor by @j4jishun is proving it. It was amazing to work with our official Event photography partner VIBGYOR photography academy 

and kudos to the video captured & edited by our director of videography @ziyaadjuolay ❤️🙏🏻 thank you ziyaad for accepting our request making us part of your life now and creating such wonderful memories for our team.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I don’t really know how to explain the sleepless nights, helpless days, street wandering to the eye sight that got triggered by the needle, all is well that ends well. 
To my first ever appearance as a fashion designer, quodos 🥂
And yes many more to go! 
Thankyou @urvishetty for being the feather to the cap!
I believe nobody else could pull that out like you !👑❤️
And lastly I’m so grateful to @riadaryani  ma’am for giving us this big opportunity and supporting all way through it! ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
मैं तो तेरी जोगनिया, 
तू जोग लगा दे रे…

I’ve been dying to create this look forever, and what better excuse than Navratri? 😩✨

By the time we started shooting this, it was almost midnight; after two intense shoots with completely different setups and makeup looks. For this one, I had to wipe off every last bit of makeup, put on a face sheet for a quick refresh, and then channel that raw, no-makeup vibe. How close do you think we got to the real deal? Let me know 🥺

Oh, and did I mention we powered through this whole shoot marathon from 2 PM to 7 AM the next morning? Between feeling like Wonder Woman and Badrakali from time and back again🥶🙈
I Can’ttt wait to show you all the BTS!

Massive shoutout to my team for sticking it out with me and my moodswings and making my vision a reality ❤️
